tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE manufacturing_integration (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    part_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    material VARCHAR(100),
    3d_printing_speed INT,
    manufacturing_process VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE 3D_Printing_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    part_name VARCHAR(255),
    material VARCHAR(100),
    print_time_hours DECIMAL(5,2),
    print_quality VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Manufacturing_Processes (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    process_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    efficiency_rating INT,
    equipment_required VARCHAR(100),
    cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Operations_Integration (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    operation_name VARCHAR(255),
    integration_type VARCHAR(50),
    processing_time_hours DECIMAL(5,2),
    success_rate DECIMAL(4,2)
);

CREATE TABLE 3d_printers (
    printer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand TEXT,
    model TEXT,
    print_technology TEXT,
    max_build_volume FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE manufacturing_processes (
    process_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    process_name TEXT,
    equipment_used TEXT,
    materials TEXT,
    labor_hours_required FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE printing_jobs (
    job_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    printer_id INT,
    process_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE materials_inventory (
    material_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    quantity INT,
    supplier TEXT,
    purchase_date DATE
)
